    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 <strong>Age of Enchantment</strong>，这是一款你一直期待的塔防、卡组构筑与 D&amp;D 的融合之作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tower Defense + Deckbuilding + D&amp;D</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神器系统</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过升级或在游戏中发现神器，并使用精华购买来解锁神器。随后，你可以在出战配置中设置它们，以帮助你最大化构筑并寻找最强大的协同效果。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>职业主题防御塔</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的防御塔以 D&amp;D 职业为原型。以战士和法师开始游戏，并在升级过程中解锁圣骑士、牧师、野蛮人和术士。每座防御塔拥有 3 条不同的升级路线，每条路线包含 3 个阶级。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112430/extras/d3b19738d0ce1fc498091b9844b1e685.poster.avif?t=1771857939\" width=1170 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112430/extras/d3b19738d0ce1fc498091b9844b1e685.webm?t=1771857939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112430/extras/d3b19738d0ce1fc498091b9844b1e685.mp4?t=1771857939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在每张地图前选择你的出战配置以定制你的策略</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设置你的防御塔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的神器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过疯狂之颅调整难度 —— 并获得巨额奖励。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112430/extras/7b0fcba42fdcd73de499a96b3d045abb.poster.avif?t=1771857939\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112430/extras/7b0fcba42fdcd73de499a96b3d045abb.webm?t=1771857939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112430/extras/7b0fcba42fdcd73de499a96b3d045abb.mp4?t=1771857939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deckbuilding</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向 RNG 之神祈祷，通过献祭卡牌来获得最适合你构筑的卡牌，或使用献祭系统移除你不需要的卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112430/extras/1d8cf6493f1a883eeabcfe8aba79b520.poster.avif?t=1771857939\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112430/extras/1d8cf6493f1a883eeabcfe8aba79b520.webm?t=1771857939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112430/extras/1d8cf6493f1a883eeabcfe8aba79b520.mp4?t=1771857939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo 内容：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最高等级 5（完整版为 20）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁 4 座防御塔（完整版为 6）</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wizard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cleric</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paladin</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 张可游玩地图（完整版为 10）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 个以疯狂之颅形式呈现的难度修饰符，它们会以具有挑战性的方式改变游戏，但会大幅提高获胜奖励（完整版为 10）</p></li></ul>",
